org.terrier.matching

Class JforestsModelMatching

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.terrier.matching.LearnedModelMatching
      • org.terrier.matching.JforestsModelMatching
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Matching

    public class JforestsModelMatching
extends LearnedModelMatching
    Applies a Jforests regression tree learned model to a FeaturedResultSet. Learned model files are generated by Jforests. If you use this class, you are implicitly using the jforests library, and the applies.

    Properties

    • fat.matching.learned.jforest.model - filename of the ensemble model generated by jforests
    • fat.matching.learned.jforest.statistics - filename of the feature statistics file generated by jforests
    Since:
    4.0
    Author:
    Craig Macdonald
